Helene Palmer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helene_Palmer 0 Helene Palmer (5 March 1928 – 5 January 2011) was a British actress best known for her portrayal of Ida Clough, a factory machinist in the long-running soap opera, Coronation Street. She appeared in the show on/off between 1978 and 1998.
